{"tid":296950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[健身撚] 我同人講一人一組share做，人地唔肯，究竟係咪我問題？","createTime":"2017-06-25T05:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T10:39:06.000Z","uid":51440,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86d3d343e3d293722c2756fd32f1bbb64b8eba00","tid":296950,"uid":51440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"今日去做gym，同個阿婆一齊行埋去部leg press機度，我讓佢做先，同佢講一人一組輪流啦，之後佢就話：我啱啱先坐底咋喎！<br />\n<br />\n我：我意思係一人一組share來做<br />\n<br />\n婆：我做夠我自然會走啦<br />\n<br />\n佢條撚樣就插最輕，係度慢慢做，之後我等左三分鐘左右我就開聲：一人一組輪住做啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n婆：我仲做緊囉，我做夠自然會走<br />\n<br />\n我：依部唔係帶氧機喎，你唔可能咁樣長時間霸住做架喎，跑步機有十幾部，依部得一部咋喎<br />\n<br />\n婆：人人都係等人做完先架啦，係得你先咁樣趕人，你咁叻你應該叫依度加機丫麻<br />\n<br />\n我：依個唔關加機事喎，係使用方法問題<br />\n<br />\n婆：咁我咁做有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n我：部部機都係咁架啦，多人要用嘅就每人做十幾廿下一組輪住做<br />\n<br />\n婆：咁我點解一定要做十幾廿下一組，每人做嘅方法都唔同啦，點解一定要跟你<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母之後我都廢撚事拗，我問佢：咁你仲要做幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n婆：我點知我要做幾耐，我做夠就會起身啦<br />\n<br />\n之後我等撚左佢十幾分鐘，佢走撚左仲要大大聲同佢啲fd講話我趕佢走，搞撚到好似我洽佢咁。屌你老母啦，彩你都攞撚哂啦，仲要屈鳩我，我幾撚時有趕你走，都話大家share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我都諗緊個問題，一組真係無話幾多下幾耐，究竟我咁樣開聲係咪我問題，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc87ca94140b27aa429a4e4a16a5d6d70f48114","tid":296950,"uid":57223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"下次幫佢插重啲等佢慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68ecee4bf37d84ee55ff0dcea45cc475e478899","tid":296950,"uid":37871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"我認同你，只係同佢嘈，一開口已經輸左。。。"},{"pid":"65ea9f4cacb7df280c1baff5643ac02c970c909d","tid":296950,"uid":51440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認同你，只係同佢嘈，一開口已經輸左。。。</blockquote><br />\n但個問題係我同佢一齊行埋去，佢都知我要用，我諗住一齊用，點知撞正個無賴"},{"pid":"2aa2de798f248d4362861ca651e4c34ce24f7a13","tid":296950,"uid":21489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"又係呢D廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e0960b9483149b3f283779c7444de076564f48","tid":296950,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"搵工作人員喇"},{"pid":"c9e02fe76e2217ad956cf77f299c18d2319ac094","tid":296950,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"佢地真係做一組,當帶氧咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eb13f564d76322c09e51218b4b4cb53417fed4","tid":296950,"uid":51440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢D廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最撚唔開心係，佢仲要做啲fd講我趕佢，果啲人仲要撐佢，聲到話理撚得佢啦，咁野蠻乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1404343814d4913ed0ee20e2fb88c0f0d111706c","tid":296950,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"所以d廢老真係唔好讓"},{"pid":"9d29a526917680ac078bc7ff6f8c5660b1aafe55","tid":296950,"uid":51440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係呢D廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最撚唔開心係，佢仲要<del>做</del>啲fd講我趕佢，果啲人仲要撐佢，聲到話理撚得佢啦，咁野蠻乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同"},{"pid":"4c77e1b969e4cafa1a9090e1834424f0b09d1967","tid":296950,"uid":119378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:2