/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔走唔通你報警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n康民我都預左，但我唔係去康民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係大場，我唔知你驚咩<br />\nSHARE就預咗，佢唔讓就搵Staff嚟，可以獨霸機嘅咩？<br />\n唔知樓豬驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係驚啲staff都話無問題，條仆街仲唔食住我上</blockquote><br />\n再講佢唔係休息唔肯讓，只不過係當帶氧咁長時間做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都想知係咪我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己唔係健身撚<br />\n但同呢班仆街嘈撚完都無mood又晒時間<br />\n不如做左其他先 最後先做個個動作/索性搵其他代左佢<br />\n因為佢唔讓你都吹佢唔漲<br />\nbtw 我唔知掉亂次序會唔會變左成套無用<br />\n唔好屌咁大力"},{"pid":"38aad71acb5635fa3f9444d02a60db9df939b5cc","tid":296950,"uid":51440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbed6edaf206d608ae69094cd8d26895fc2a2298","tid":296950,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>廢老，玩得康文預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔走唔通你報警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n康民我都預左，但我唔係去康民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係大場，我唔知你驚咩<br />\nSHARE就預咗，佢唔讓就搵Staff嚟，可以獨霸機嘅咩？<br />\n唔知樓豬驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係驚啲staff都話無問題，條仆街仲唔食住我上</blockquote><br />\n再講佢唔係休息唔肯讓，只不過係當帶氧咁長時間做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都想知係咪我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都明白<br />\n唯有當唔好彩,做其他<br />\n<br />\n佢地一路做唔停,冇得話霸住部機<br />\n搵職員,職員都唔知可以講乜"},{"pid":"3dd154a85ac09ef0c3655e4f6cc9371bf993